## 📋 Summary

| Operator Type | Purpose | Syntax Example |
|---|---|---|
| **Arithmetic** | Math calculations | `$((A + B))` |
| **Relational** | Numeric comparison | `[ $A -gt $B ]` |
| **String Compare** | String equality | `[ "$A" == "$B" ]` |
| **Logical AND** | Both must be true | `[ cond1 ] && [ cond2 ]` |
| **Logical OR** | Either must be true | `[ cond1 ] \|\| [ cond2 ]` |

